Who knows, one day, maybe I'll be able to.

157
00:13:17,672 --> 00:13:19,715
不过我希望你们知道
But I want you both to know,

158
00:13:19,757 --> 00:13:26,806
你们就在这里, 永远, 任何时候
that you're right here, always, all the time.

159
00:13:31,644 --> 00:13:35,231
抱歉Teyla. 即使以最快速度飞行
我们也只是刚刚比它们的舰队提前一点
Sorry Teyla. Even flying full out,
we're just ahead of the armada.

160
00:13:35,273 --> 00:13:37,775
我不能冒险下去接Oren和他的家人
I can't risk putting down for Oren or his family.

161
00:13:37,817 --> 00:13:39,193
知道了
I see.

162
00:13:40,695 --> 00:13:43,781
我准备让我们脱离隐形状态, 以穿过星际之门
拨号吧
I'm gonna take us out of stealth mode for the pass.
Dial the gate.

163
00:13:48,202 --> 00:13:50,121
等一下! 有虫洞连接进来!
Hang on! Incoming wormhole!

164
00:13:57,795 --> 00:13:59,755
我听过一些故事
