I have heard stories of the Wraith dialling in,

165
00:13:59,797 --> 00:14:02,884
以阻止受害人
通过星际之门逃跑
to prevent their victims from
using the Stargate as a means of escape.

166
00:14:02,925 --> 00:14:04,719
这么说我们滞留在这里了
So we're stuck here.

167
00:14:05,219 --> 00:14:08,806
只要让这艘飞船再次处于隐形状态
我们就会非常安全
Once the ship is rendered invisible again,
we will be perfectly safe.

168
00:14:08,848 --> 00:14:11,934
我更担心的是, 不久以后
幽灵的舰队就会抵达亚特兰蒂斯
I'm more worried about getting the intel
about the Wraith fleet back to Atlantis.

169
00:14:12,059 --> 00:14:14,937
我们至少可以整个晚上
不断的拨号
Then we'll keep dialling in through
the night at the very least.

170
00:14:15,938 --> 00:14:19,609
不过如果我们等在
我告诉Oren 和他家人的那个地方...
But if we wait in the location
I told Oren and his family to meet us...

171
00:14:19,650 --> 00:14:21,944
我正在赶往那里
That's where I'm headed.

172
00:14:31,120 --> 00:14:33,164
我必须提醒你
我并不是很擅长做这种事情
