I'm not very good at this sort of thing.

173
00:14:33,289 --> 00:14:35,666
不用担心
这个只有你和你的家人才会看到
Well don't worry. The only people
that's gonna see it, is you and your family.

174
00:14:35,791 --> 00:14:38,127
是的, 还有你和美国军方
Aye, and you and the US military.

175
00:14:38,503 --> 00:14:39,921
准备好了么?
Give it a shot?

176
00:14:40,254 --> 00:14:41,631
