178
00:14:46,802 --> 00:14:48,471
我希望谁在这里?
I wish who was here?

179
00:14:48,513 --> 00:14:49,931
我不知道. 你希望谁在这里?
I don't know. Who do you wish was here?

180
00:14:49,972 --> 00:14:52,016
没有谁! 我只希望我不在这里!
Nobody! I wish I wasn't bloody here!

181
00:14:52,058 --> 00:14:53,935
博士, 我还有很多人要去拍呢
Doc, I got a lotta people I gotta get through.

182
00:14:55,228 --> 00:14:59,982
好吧, 嗯, 我想
我可以向我的母亲问好
Alright, uh, I suppose
I could say hello to my Mother.

183
00:15:00,066 --> 00:15:03,319
