Hello Mum! I hope this message finds you well.

187
00:15:10,493 --> 00:15:14,413
我相信你的牵牛花现在正在盛开
I trust your petunia's are in full bloom by now.

188
00:15:14,539 --> 00:15:17,917
噢, 我真希望
你还在用我给你的那些药膏
Oh, and I do hope you're keeping up
with the ointment I gave you.

189
00:15:18,042 --> 00:15:21,629
