No, no, I can't do that. I'll get all emotional.

196
00:15:36,018 --> 00:15:37,061
是么?
So?

197
00:15:37,645 --> 00:15:41,774
我的妈妈, 她非常的敏感
就像你碰到的最美好的灵魂
She's very delicate, my mother.
As sweet a soul as you'll ever meet.

