00:15:41,941 --> 00:15:46,904
跟刚刚飘落的雪花一样纯洁 如果我很不安
那么她也会不安, 所以我不能这样做
As pure as the driven snow. If I get upset
then she'll get upset, and I can't have that.

199
00:15:46,988 --> 00:15:48,739
我们并不是在现场直播, 博士
It's not like we're live Doc.

200
00:15:48,865 --> 00:15:51,701
如果你不喜欢我们录在带子上的东西
我们可以再来一次
I mean, you don't like what we put on tape
the first time,we can always do it again.

201
00:15:51,742 --> 00:15:54,036
- 可以么?
- 当然
- We can?
- Sure.

202
00:15:54,328 --> 00:15:58,207
噢  那么我想我可以了
Oh. I suppose I could do that then.

203
00:15:59,083 --> 00:16:02,378
好吧, 我们开始吧
Alright, here we go.

204
00:16:06,215 --> 00:16:07,675
妈妈...
Mum...

205
00:16:11,762 --> 00:16:13,848
我真是太想你了
I miss you terribly.

206
00:16:18,102 --> 00:16:19,729
我做不到!
I can't do this!

207
00:16:33,159 --> 00:16:35,244
来啊Oren, 快点出现!
Come on Oren, show up!

208
00:16:39,457 --> 00:16:40,750
怎么了?
What?

209
00:16:40,958 --> 00:16:43,794
就在不久前, 你还非常乐意他们丢下
Not long ago you would have blithely left them behind.

210
00:16:43,920 --> 00:16:46,172
好吧, 现在情况不同了
Well the situation has changed.

211
00:16:49,383 --> 00:16:52,970
今天早些时候, Ford中尉建议
我们去偷一群孩子
Earlier today Lt Ford suggested
we steal from a community of children.

212
00:16:53,137 --> 00:16:55,723
那是因为他们有ZPM
我们可以把他们一齐带回来
That's because they have a ZPM
and we can bring them back.

213
00:16:55,890 --> 00:16:58,309
到亚特兰蒂斯来等死?
Only to face death in Atlantis?

214
00:16:59,519 --> 00:17:03,856
我和Ford都是军人
我们牺牲了无数条生命来学会如何生存
Look, Ford and I are military. We've spent
a lot of our lives learning how to survive.

215
00:17:03,940 --> 00:17:06,108
我整个一生都在学习
如何在幽灵的威胁下生存
I've spent my life surviving the Wraith.

216
00:17:06,150 --> 00:17:10,238
训练的一部分就是要明白
哪些人你可以救, 哪些你不能
Part of that training is knowing who
you can save and who you can't.

217
00:17:10,363 --> 00:17:12,573
然后决定就是你们自己?
And that decision is yours alone?

218
00:17:12,865 --> 00:17:16,118
我说过如果有时间, 我会等你的朋友
I said that I'd wait for your friend if there was time.

219
00:17:16,244 --> 00:17:19,956
现在就有时间
你还想要我做什么?
Now there's time. What else do you want from me?

220
00:17:21,707 --> 00:17:23,709
我实在是太害怕了
Too much I fear.

221
00:17:25,878 --> 00:17:28,005
这将会是一个漫长的夜晚
It's gonna be a long night.

222
00:18:38,451 --> 00:18:42,788
你并没有说那需要安全许可 是不是?
You didn't say anything that would
require security clearance did you?

223
00:18:42,830 --> 00:18:45,374
安全许可?
Security clearance?

224
00:18:54,759 --> 00:18:56,969
只能在这里坐视不管, 实在是受不了
This is hard, to sit and watch.

225
00:18:57,512 --> 00:18:58,763
我们什么也做不了
There's nothing you can do.

226
00:18:58,763 --> 00:19:00,765
我们可以做很多事
We can do a lot.

227
00:19:00,806 --> 00:19:03,059
