But if we save Oren and his family,
we will have done something.

230
00:19:14,362 --> 00:19:16,739
某些事
Something.

231
00:19:20,868 --> 00:19:22,411
我会想你的kiddo
I'm gonna miss you kiddo.

232
00:19:22,453 --> 00:19:25,665
我等不住想马上回到家里
带你去看篮球比赛
I can't wait to get back home and
take you to a basketball game.

233
00:19:25,665 --> 00:19:31,420
看着科比和奥尼尔
为湖人再赢得一次冠军
Watch Kobe and Shaq take
another title home for the Lakers.

234
00:19:34,507 --> 00:19:36,634
就这
That's it.

235
00:19:37,009 --> 00:19:38,761
就这?
That's it?

236
00:19:39,262 --> 00:19:40,638
我还可以对孩子说些什么
What else am I gonna say to the kid.

237
00:19:40,638 --> 00:19:41,806
是你的小弟弟SGT?
It's your little brother SGT.

238
00:19:41,848 --> 00:19:45,059
我可能再也见不着他了
为什么要让事情变得更糟呢
And I'm probably never gonna see him again,
why make it worse than it has to be.

239
00:19:45,101 --> 00:19:49,105
- 那跟这个无关!
- 那就是这样做的目的
- That's not what this is about man!
- That's exactly what this is about.

240
00:19:51,566 --> 00:19:53,025
别担心, 中尉
Don't sweat it Lt.

241
00:19:53,067 --> 00:19:54,902
我很高兴我有机会说再见
I'm happy I got the chance to say goodbye.

242
00:19:54,944 --> 00:19:56,904
是的, 不过你并没有说
Yeah, but you didn't say it.

243
00:19:57,071 --> 00:20:00,241
要说的话太多
Not in so many words.

244
00:20:06,289 --> 00:20:07,164
Ford中尉!
Lt Ford!

245
00:20:07,206 --> 00:20:09,083
啊, 你准备好录制你的消息了?
Ah, you ready to record your message?

246
00:20:09,125 --> 00:20:10,418
差不多已经完了
Already done.

247
00:20:10,418 --> 00:20:13,129
实际上我利用特权私下为自己录好了
Actually I took the liberty of doing mine in private.

248
00:20:13,171 --> 00:20:15,214
可能需要一些编辑
Now it may require some editing.

249
00:20:15,256 --> 00:20:15,840
编辑
Editing.

250
00:20:15,882 --> 00:20:18,676
