Yeah, I went on a bit.
Actually I used the entire tape.

251
00:20:18,718 --> 00:20:19,760
你讲了一个小时?
You talked for an hour.

252
00:20:19,802 --> 00:20:22,013
事实上, 我发现这很有治疗作用
See, I found it rather therapeutic actually.

253
00:20:22,054 --> 00:20:26,350
我很自信, 我提出了一些很有价值的观点
事实上, 我非常确信
Now I'm fairly confident I've come up
with several valuable insights. In fact I'm sure of it,

254
00:20:26,392 --> 00:20:29,312
不过最近几天我只睡了六个小时
but I've only slept six hours in the last few days.

255
00:20:29,353 --> 00:20:30,813
这是给谁的?
Who's it for?

256
00:20:30,946 --> 00:20:32,690
总体来说, 是给我妹妹的
Humanity in general, my sister. Look,

