cut off, fine, but if the gate holds the connection a few extra
milliseconds then we won't have wasted the time.

259
00:20:43,492 --> 00:20:44,660
我也很期盼这样
I look forward to it.

260
00:20:44,660 --> 00:20:47,205
好吧, 好好欣赏吧
Well, enjoy.

261
00:20:48,039 --> 00:20:49,832
金子
Gold.

