00:35:16,782 --> 00:35:19,911
她知道我来自地球, 这不是什么该死的秘密
She knows I'm from Earth son, it's not a bloody secret.

426
00:35:19,952 --> 00:35:20,620
哦, 对
Oh, right.

427
00:35:20,912 --> 00:35:23,080
对不起妈妈... 不管怎样
Sorry mum... anyhow.

428
00:35:23,122 --> 00:35:26,209
授权使用囚犯来测试一种实验药品
Authorized using a prisoner
to test an experimental drug,

429
00:35:26,250 --> 00:35:28,794
这显然违反了日内瓦协约
in clear violation of the Geneva convention.

430
00:35:28,836 --> 00:35:30,588
授权降下星际之门防护盾
Authorized lowering the Stargate shield

431
00:35:30,630 --> 00:35:34,467
当准备进入的人的身份
受到明显质疑的时候
when the authenticity of
incoming travellers was clearly in question.

432
00:35:34,634 --> 00:35:37,178
还有一处风景
我在临死前没有能够看到
That's another sight I'll die without having seen.

433
00:35:37,178 --> 00:35:41,265
如果你像我一样旅行了这么远
你会发现想念尼亚加拉瀑布
也不是什么大不了的事情
See, to be fair - when you've travelled
as much as I've travelled, you'd think that
missing Niagra Falls would be no big deal.

434
00:35:41,307 --> 00:35:43,059
不过你知道么? 这种思念不停的折磨你
But you know what? It gnaws at you.

435
00:35:43,100 --> 00:35:46,103
还有很多电影我都想看
不过我现在看不成了
Alot of movies I wish I'd seen, that I won't see now.

436
00:35:46,145 --> 00:35:48,981
从来没有看过Grease, 既便是
我在还是一个孩子的时候就已经有了
一个Olivia Newton John的纪念品
Never saw Grease even though I had a thing
for Olivia Newton John when I was a kid.

437
00:35:49,023 --> 00:35:55,655
我一直都想看Ghandi,
我只看了《第六感》的前半部分
一直想知道它是怎样收尾的
I always wanted to see Ghandi, only saw the first half
of the Sixth Sense, always wondered how that ended.

438
00:35:55,696 --> 00:35:58,157
我的妹妹...
My sister...

439
00:35:58,574 --> 00:36:03,913
Ford, 如果你把其它部分剪掉了
一定要把这部分留下, 好么?
Ford if you cut everything else,
just keep this part okay?

440
00:36:04,455 --> 00:36:09,836
Jenny, 我是你的哥哥Rodney. 很显然
Jenny, it's your brother Rodney. Obviously.

441
00:36:10,253 --> 00:36:14,006
我想说, 嗯...
I wanna say, umm...

442
00:36:14,048 --> 00:36:17,093
我想说些什么
I wanna say something.

443
00:36:18,261 --> 00:36:21,097
家人很重要
Family is important.

444
00:36:21,347 --> 00:36:27,478
我意识到这一点是因为, 这里的人们
在某种程度上, 在心理上充当了家人的地位
I've come to realize that because the people here
have become a sort of surrogate family to me.

445
00:36:27,520 --> 00:36:32,066
现在我知道你在想些什么
我从来不会去鼓吹那种情感, 不过...
Now I know what you're thinking, I've never been
the poster child for that kind of sentiment but...

446
00:36:32,108 --> 00:36:39,782
当某个人即将面临死亡的时候
他看到的事物也更加透彻
when one's contemplating their own demise,
one sees things more clearly.

447
00:36:39,949 --> 00:36:42,618
我真心地祝你好, 你知道
I really do wish you the best, you know.

448
00:36:42,660 --> 00:36:44,954
我很抱歉我们无法更加亲近
And I'm sorry we weren't closer.

449
00:36:44,996 --> 00:36:46,831
也许, ...
Perhaps, ...

450
00:36:48,875 --> 00:36:52,378
如果我有机会度过这次难关
也许某一天我们就可以
if by chance I make it out of this,
perhaps one day we can be.

451
00:36:52,420 --> 00:36:54,922
我也很想这样
And I would like that.

452
00:36:55,339 --> 00:37:01,971
现在, 如果还有时间, 我想回到
领导能力这个主题上来
Now, if there's time, I'd like to go
back to the subject of leadership.

453
00:37:03,306 --> 00:37:05,850
有人过来了
Someone's coming.

454
00:37:20,031 --> 00:37:22,241
Oren!
Oren!

455
00:37:23,075 --> 00:37:23,451
Oren!
Oren!

456
00:37:23,492 --> 00:37:24,952
这个家庭到底有多大?
How big is his family?

457
00:37:24,994 --> 00:37:26,704
他们在路上一定碰到了其他人
They must have met up with others along the way.

458
00:37:26,746 --> 00:37:28,331
这会是一个问题
That's gonna be a problem.

459
00:37:28,372 --> 00:37:30,166
我无法想象你们还在这里
I didn't think you'd still be here.

460
00:37:30,166 --> 00:37:31,417
我们不会丢下你的
We would not have gone without you.

461
00:37:31,459 --> 00:37:34,754
我们发现其他人正在路上
还有更多人在更后面
We found others on the way,
and even more further behind.

462
00:37:34,754 --> 00:37:36,130
还有多少人?
How many more?

463
00:37:36,172 --> 00:37:38,633
十二个, 可能更多
Twelve, perhaps more.

464
00:37:38,674 --> 00:37:40,426
这里
In here,

465
00:37:40,676 --> 00:37:44,305
这边! 快点!
this way! Quickly!

466
00:37:44,347 --> 00:37:47,475
等, 等, 等, 等, 等一下!
Wait, wait, wait, wait, wait!

467
00:37:52,939 --> 00:37:54,607
好了, 我们会尽可能多的多带些人!
Alright, we'll fit as many people as we can!

468
00:37:54,649 --> 00:37:57,235
快点, 来吧!
Hurry, come on!

469
00:37:58,027 --> 00:38:00,655
一直向前! 一直向前!
Straight ahead! Straight ahead!

470
00:38:04,075 --> 00:38:05,743
赶快!
Hurry!

471
00:38:10,206 --> 00:38:11,040
没事的
It's alright.

472
00:38:11,249 --> 00:38:12,375
没事的
It's alright.

473
00:39:21,569 --> 00:39:24,197
我们的客人已经安置好了么?
Are our guests comfortably settled in?

474
00:39:24,405 --> 00:39:25,364
是的
Yes.

475
00:39:25,406 --> 00:39:26,782
很好
Good.

476
00:39:28,492 --> 00:39:29,994
告诉我
So tell me,

477
00:39:30,661 --> 00:39:32,330
到底有多糟糕?
how bad is it?

478
00:39:32,663 --> 00:39:33,915
很糟糕
Bad.

479
00:39:36,125 --> 00:39:40,129
每艘母船就像是一艘航空母舰
Each hive ship acts like a carrier group with

480
00:39:40,171 --> 00:39:43,758
大舰以及数以百计的小飞船守卫在周围
cruisers and hundreds of darts escorting it.

481
00:39:43,799 --> 00:39:47,595
Groden现在正在下载探测器上的读数
Groden's downloading the sensor readings right now.

482
00:39:47,637 --> 00:39:50,556
我从没有看到过一次洗劫带走了这么多人
I've never witnessed a culling that took so many.

483
00:39:50,640 --> 00:39:55,019
我们救出了一些人, 这还是值得肯定的
We saved a few, that's worth something.

484
00:39:55,645 --> 00:39:57,813
Rodney, 我们准备好发送消息了么?
Rodney, are we ready to send our message?

485
00:39:57,855 --> 00:39:58,981
随时都可以
When you are.

486
00:39:59,023 --> 00:40:01,108
OK
OK.

487
00:40:07,782 --> 00:40:12,245
Ford中尉刚刚完成为每个探险队成员
记录个人消息的工作
Lieutenant Ford is just finishing recording
personal messages from all the team members,

488
00:40:12,286 --> 00:40:12,912
如果你愿意?
if you'd like?

489
00:40:12,954 --> 00:40:15,206
我很好
I'm good.

490
00:40:15,790 --> 00:40:16,791
好吧
Okay.

491
00:40:16,832 --> 00:40:18,751
在我个人的一点简短的说明之后
Well along with a short note of my own,

492
00:40:18,751 --> 00:40:22,421
我还顺便为我们失去的人的家人
录上了一些话
I took the liberty of recording messages
for the families of the people we've lost.

493
00:40:22,421 --> 00:40:23,214
这是个好主意
That's a good idea.

494
00:40:23,214 --> 00:40:25,174
不过还有一个特别的人
But there's one in particular,

495
00:40:25,216 --> 00:40:30,054
我想也许应该由你自己来完成
I thought maybe you'd might like to do for yourself.

496
00:40:34,475 --> 00:40:37,687
OK, 只要你准备好了, 长官
随时可以开始
Okay, whenever you're ready Sir. Go ahead.

497
00:40:38,187 --> 00:40:42,859
我不知道Sumner上校的家人
是否还活着
I'm not sure if Colonel Sumner's
parents are still alive.

498
00:40:42,900 --> 00:40:47,154
我甚至不知道他是否还留有一个家庭
我们大家都不知道
I'm not even sure he has
a family back there, not all of us do.

499
00:40:47,196 --> 00:40:49,657
不过如果他确实有一个家庭
But if he does have a family,

500
00:40:49,657 --> 00:40:52,493
他们应该知道他带着 ...
they should know that he died with ...

501
00:40:52,535 --> 00:40:57,498
荣耀和勇气在完成他的任务的时候牺牲了
honour and courage in the perfomance of his duty.

502
00:40:57,582 --> 00:41:03,337
他担负着领导的重担
而且他做得很出色
He carried the burden of a leader,
and he carried it well.

503
00:41:03,421 --> 00:41:07,175
我没有机会更深入的了解他, 不过 ...
I didn't get the chance to know him well, but ...

504
00:41:07,175 --> 00:41:09,677
我所知道的是
I know this,

505
00:41:09,719 --> 00:41:15,057
考虑到他作为男人的品格
以及我们即将面对的敌人
considering the type of man
he was and what we're up against,

506
00:41:15,099 --> 00:41:19,604
我希望他仍然在这里
yeah I wish he was still here.

507
00:41:19,604 --> 00:41:23,649
我无时无刻不在想你Simon
Not a day goes by that I don't think of you Simon.

508
00:41:23,691 --> 00:41:26,277
实在是有太多的事情想跟你说
There's so much I want to tell you

509
00:41:26,319 --> 00:41:28,738
以及跟你分享
and share with you.

510
00:41:28,905 --> 00:41:31,490
不过我不能
But I can't.

511
00:41:32,617 --> 00:41:35,244
我知道这不公平
I know this is unfair,

512
00:41:35,286 --> 00:41:37,538
那么多东西你都不知道
so much you don't know,

513
00:41:37,580 --> 00:41:41,417
但你却要在生活中支持我
and putting your life on hold for me.

514
00:41:43,044 --> 00:41:45,922
所以不要这样了
So don't,

515
00:41:45,963 --> 00:41:49,675
我要你做的就是照顾好自己
all I ask is that you take care of yourself.

516
00:41:49,717 --> 00:41:52,803
不管你在哪里
And know that wherever you are,

517
00:41:52,845 --> 00:41:56,140
我的心会一直同你在一起
my heart is looking after you.

518
00:41:56,599 --> 00:41:58,392
照顾好你自己
So take care of yourself,

519
00:41:58,434 --> 00:41:59,810
多睡眠
lots of sleep

520
00:41:59,852 --> 00:42:01,812
记住每天散步
and remember your daily walks,

521
00:42:01,812 --> 00:42:04,565
坚持按你的药方服药
and keep up with your prescription.

522
00:42:04,607 --> 00:42:06,734
就是这些
Well that's about it,

523
00:42:06,776 --> 00:42:08,945
现在我要说再见了
I'll say goodbye now.

524
00:42:10,196 --> 00:42:12,114
妈妈
And mum,

525
00:42:12,365 --> 00:42:13,824
我真的很爱你
I do love you.

526
00:42:14,075 --> 00:42:16,744
再见, 爷爷, 奶奶 - 我想你们!
Bye Grandma, Grandpa - I miss you!

527
00:42:17,036 --> 00:42:18,246
再见, 弟弟!
Goodbye bro!

528
00:42:21,874 --> 00:42:22,708
再见
Goodbye.

529
00:42:23,417 --> 00:42:25,378
再见, Simon
Goodbye Simon.

530
00:42:26,671 --> 00:42:27,755
再见
Goodbye.

531
00:42:36,639 --> 00:42:40,393
我们收到了计划外的连接!
We have unscheduled offworld activation!

532
00:42:43,896 --> 00:42:45,648
接收传输
Receiving transmission.

533
00:42:49,902 --> 00:42:51,571
来自哪里?
Who's it from?

534
00:42:53,698 --> 00:42:55,241
亚特兰蒂斯


Atlantis.

